01:35:33.743 --> 01:35:35.953
My birthplace, Cosenza, Italy.

1496
01:35:36.079 --> 01:35:37.205
That's him.

1497
01:35:37.330 --> 01:35:38.414
And my name...

1498
01:35:38.498 --> 01:35:41.000
That's Heller.
...will be Primo Sparazza.

1499
01:35:42.377 --> 01:35:45.129
Now, gentlemen, I understand
that this is a dramatic approach.

1500
01:35:45.213 --> 01:35:48.216
He went deep cover in 1940. He
could have ripped the Mafia apart.

1501
01:35:48.299 --> 01:35:49.341
But I firmly believe...

1502
01:35:49.425 --> 01:35:51.718
Dismantled most of the
organized crime in this country.

1503
01:35:51.803 --> 01:35:55.264
...this is the only way to
truly infiltrate organized crime.

1504
01:35:55.348 --> 01:35:58.768
His superiors were convinced
that he had gone rogue,

1505
01:35:58.852 --> 01:36:00.186
swapped allegiances,

1506
01:36:00.270 --> 01:36:02.355
