1519
01:36:48.860 --> 01:36:52.405
Until now. Heller's op
predated the second World War.

1520
01:36:52.488 --> 01:36:54.364
About 60 years
of amassed intel.

1521
01:36:54.449 --> 01:36:56.993
Do you have any idea
of how valuable that is?

1522
01:36:57.076 --> 01:36:58.160
Yeah.

1523
01:37:00.163 --> 01:37:01.539
